import React from "react"
import {FormHolder,FieldHolder,Input,TextArea,Button} from "../style"
const Register = () =>{
    return <FormHolder>
        <FieldHolder>
            <Input type="text" name="firstName" placeholder="First Name" width={"47%"}/>
            <Input type="text" name="lastName" placeholder="Last Name" width={"47%"}/>
        </FieldHolder>
        <FieldHolder>
            <Input type="number" name="cnic" placeholder="CNIC without dashes" width={"47%"}/>
            <Input type="number" name="contactNo" placeholder="Contact No" width={"47%"}/>
        </FieldHolder>
        <FieldHolder>
            <TextArea width={"100%"} placeholder="Address" rows={5}/>
        </FieldHolder>
        <FieldHolder>
            <Button name="register" value="Register" width={"47%"} />
        </FieldHolder>
    </FormHolder>
}
export default Register
